    "Due to the limited evidence on the technological requirements of DPPs, and to avoid potential technological conflicts, we proactively proceeded by processing and working with published material closer to the time period of DPPs publications, an action also validated in [23].The Google Scholar platform was used for the collection of the literature due to the high quantity and quality of the available academic and research material."
